---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title={"Lower Your Prescription Costs | AltaMedicare"}
  description={"Free prescription review for Utah Medicare beneficiaries. We compare your medications across Part D plans and pharmacies to find your lowest cost."}
  canonical="/drug-savings.html"
>

<section class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="index.html">Home</a> &nbsp;&rsaquo;&nbsp; Drug Savings</div>
    <h1>Lower Your Prescription Costs</h1>
    <p class="lede">Send us your medication list and we&rsquo;ll review whether your current plan is your most affordable option. No cost. No obligation.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-white">
  <div class="container content-narrow">
    <h2>Why Most People Overpay for Prescriptions</h2>
    <p>The same medication can cost wildly different amounts depending on:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Which Part D plan you have</strong> &mdash; each plan covers different drugs at different copay tiers</li>
      <li><strong>Which pharmacy you use</strong> &mdash; preferred pharmacies often cost dramatically less than standard ones</li>
      <li><strong>Whether you use mail order</strong> &mdash; 90-day supplies are often cheaper than three monthly fills</li>
      <li><strong>Whether you qualify for Extra Help</strong> &mdash; many people qualify and don&rsquo;t know it</li>
      <li><strong>Whether the new $2,000 cap applies to you</strong> &mdash; this 2025+ change affects high-cost drug users</li>
    </ul>
    <p>People often switch into the same plan year after year out of habit. We&rsquo;ll actually compare your options, not just renew you into what you had.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="prescription-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">Free Service</span>
      <h2>Get Your Free Prescription Review</h2>
      <p>Tell us what you take and we&rsquo;ll get back to you with a personalized cost comparison.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="form-card contact-actions">
      <div class="contact-action">
        <div class="icon-circle" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="22" height="22"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-action-text">
          <strong>Text your meds to Bret</strong>
          <span>Fastest way &mdash; opens a text with your list already started</span>
        </div>
        <a href="sms:18013680700?body=Hi%20Bret%2C%20can%20you%20review%20my%20prescription%20costs%3F%20My%20medications%20are%3A%0D%0A" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Text Your Medications</a>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-action">
        <div class="icon-circle" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="22" height="22"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><path d="M22 6l-10 7L2 6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-action-text">
          <strong>Email your meds to Bret</strong>
          <span>Opens your email with a quick template to fill in</span>
        </div>
        <a href="mailto:bret@altahealthins.com?subject=Free%20Prescription%20Review&body=Name%3A%0D%0APhone%3A%0D%0AZIP%3A%0D%0APreferred%20Pharmacy%3A%0D%0A%0D%0AMedications%20(one%20per%20line%2C%20with%20dose%20if%20known)%3A%0D%0A" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">Email Your Medications</a>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-muted); text-align:center; margin:18px 0 0;">
        Bret personally reviews every list &mdash; usually within a few hours. No cost, no obligation.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="final-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Have Questions? Let's Talk.</h2>
    <p>One free, no-pressure call &mdash; clear answers, no sales pitch.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Schedule Consultation</a>
      <a href="tel:8013680700" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">Call (801) 368-0700</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</MainLayout>
